Name: analytracks
Version: 0.2.1.9
Summary: This python package contains tools to handle sport gps tracks (tcx, gpx, ...)
Home-page: http://www.olbecke.eu/research
Author: Dimitri de Smet
Author-email: dimitri.desmet@uclouvain.be
